quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  16,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  16,1,"aa gaya Allah ka faisla, ab is ke liye jaldi nah machao pak hai woh aur baala tar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log kar rahay hain"
  16,2,"woh iss rooh ko apne jis bande par chahta hai apne hukum se mulaika ke zariye nazil farma deta hai ( iss hadaayat ke sath ke logon ko )"" aagah kar do, mere siwa koi tumhara mabood nahi hai, lehaza tum mujhi se daro """
  16,3,"uss ne aasman o zameen ko brhq peda kya hai, woh bohat baala o bartar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log karte hain"
  16,4,uss ne ensaan ko aik zara si boond se peda kya aur dekhte dekhte srihan woh aik jhagralu hasti ban gaya
  16,5,"is ne janwar peda kiye jin mein tumahray liye poshak bhi hai aur khoraak bhi, aur terhan terhan ke dosray faiday bhi"
  16,6,unn mein tumahray liye jamal hai jab ke subah tum inhen charnay ke liye bhaijtay ho aur jabkay shaam inhen wapas laatay ho
  16,7,woh tumahray liye boojh dho (Lad) kar aisay aisay maqamat taq le jatay hain jahan tum sakht jaanfishani ke baghair nahi poanch satke haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhara rab bara hi shafeeq aur meharban hai
  16,8,uss ne ghoray aur khachar aur gadhay peda kiye taakay tum un par sawaar ho aur woh tumhari zindagi ki ronaqe banin woh aur bohat si cheezein ( tumahray faiday ke liye ) peda karta hai jin ka tumhe ilm taq nahi hai
  16,9,aur Allah hi ke zimma hai seedha rasta batana jab ke rastay tirhhe bhi mojood hain agar woh chahta to tum sab ko hadaayat day deta
  16,10,wohi hai jis ne aasman se tumahray liye pani barsaya jis se tum khud bhi sairaab hotay ho aur tumahray janwaron ke liye bhi charah peda hota hai
  16,11,woh is pani ke zareya se khityan ugata hai aur Zaitoon aur khajoor aur angoor aur terhan terhan ke dosray phal peda karta hai iss mein aik barri nishani hai unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar karte hain
  16,12,uss ne tumhari bhalai ke liye raat aur din ko aur Sooraj aur chaand ko maskhar kar rakha hai aur sab tarre bhi usi ke hukum se maskhar hain iss mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain
  16,13,"aur yeh jo bohat si rang barang ki cheezein is ne tumahray liye zameen mein peda kar rakhi hain, inn mein bhi zaroor nishani hai unn logon ke liye jo sabaq haasil karne walay hain"
  16,14,wohi hai jis ne tumahray liye samandar ko maskhar kar rakha hai taakay tum is se taro taaza gosht le kar khao aur is se zeenat ki woh cheezein nikalu jinhein tum pehna karte ho tum dekhte ho ke kashti samandar ka seenah cheertihui chalti hai yeh sab kuch is liye hai ke tum apne rab ka fazl talaash karo aur is ke shukar guzaar bano
  16,15,uss ne zameen mein pahoron ki maikhain garh den taakay zameen tum ko le kar dhalak nah jaye is ne daal riya jari kiye aur qudrati rastay banaye taakay tum hadaayat pao
  16,16,"is ne zameen mein rasta bitanay wali alamtain rakh den, aur taron se bhi log hadaayat paate hain"
  16,17,"phir kya woh jo peda karta hai aur woh jo kuch bhi peda nahi karte, dono yaksaa hain? kya tum hosh mein nahi atay ?"
  16,18,"agar tum Allah ki nematon ko ginna chaho to gun nahi satke, haqeeqat yeh hai ke woh bara hi dar guzar karne wala aur Raheem hai"
  16,19,halaank woh tumahray khulay se bhi waaqif hai aur chupay se bhi
  16,20,"aur woh doosri hastiyan jinhein Allah ko chore kar log pkarte hain, woh kisi cheez ki bhi khaaliq nahi hain balkay khud makhlooq hain"
  16,21,murda hain nah ke zindah aur un ko kuch maloom nahi hai ke inhen kab ( dobarah zindah kar ke ) uthaya jaye ga
  16,22,tumhara khuda bas aik hi khuda hai magar jo log akhirat ko nahi mantay unn ke dilon mein inkaar bas kar reh gaya hai aur woh ghamand mein par gay hain
  16,23,Allah yaqeenan inn ke sab kartoot jaanta hai chupay hue bhi aur khulay hue bhi woh unn logon ko hargiz pasand nahi karta jo ghuroor nafs mein mubtala hon
  16,24,"aur jab koi un se puchta hai ke tumahray rab ne yeh kya cheez nazil ki hai, to kehte hain"" aji woh to aglay waqton ki farsodah kahaniyan hain """
  16,25,"yeh baatein woh is liye karte hain ke qayamat ke roz apne boojh bhi poooray athayin, aur sath sath kuch unn logon ke boojh bhi samaiten jinhein yeh Bar banaye jahalat gumraah kar rahay hain dekho! kaisi sakht zimma daari hai jo yeh apne sir le rahay hain"
  16,26,"inn se pehlay bhi bohat se log ( haq ko neecha dikhaane ke liye ) aisi hi makaryan kar chuke hain, to dekh lau ke Allah ne unn ke makr ki imarat jarr se ukhaar pehnki aur is ki chhat oopar se un ke sir par aa rahi aur aisay rukh se un par azaab aaya jidhar se is ke anay ka unn ko gumaan taq nah tha"
  16,27,"phir qayamat ke roz Allah unhen zaleel o khawar kere ga aur unn se kahe ga"" batao ab kahan hain mere woh shareek jin ke liye tum ( ahal haq se ) jhagrre kya karte thay ?"" jin logon ko duniya mein ilm haasil tha woh kahin ge"" aaj ruswai aur badbakhti hai kafiroon ke liye """
  16,28,"haan, inhi kafiroon ke liye jo apne nafs par zulm karte hue jab mulaika ke hathon girftar hotay hain to ( sar kashi chore kar ) foran dagain (hatyar)daal dete hain aur kehte hain"" hum to koi qasoor nahi kar rahay thay"" mulaika jawab dete hain"" kar kaisay nahi rahay thay! Allah tumahray krtoton se khoob waaqif hai"
  16,29,"ab jao, jahannum ke darwazon mein ghis jao wahein tum ko hamesha rehna hai"" pas haqeeqat yeh hai ke bara hi bura thikana hai mtkbron ke liye"
  16,30,"doosri taraf jab khuda taras logon se poocha jata hai ke yeh kya cheez hai jo tumahray rab ki taraf se nazil hui hai, to woh jawab dete hain ke"" behtareen cheez utri hai"" iss terhan ke nekokaar logon ke liye iss duniya mein bhi bhalai hai aur akhirat ka ghar to zaroor hi un ke haq mein behtar hai bara acha ghar hai Muttaqiyun ka"
  16,31,"daimi qiyam ki jannaten, jin mein woh daakhil hon ge, neechay nhrin beh rahi hongi, aur sab kuch wahan ain unn ki khwahish ke mutabiq hoga yeh jaza deta hai Allah Muttaqiyun ko"
  16,32,"unn Muttaqiyun ko jin ki roohein pakizgee ki haalat mein jab mulaika qabz karte hain to kehte hain"" salam ho tum par, jao jannat mein apne aamaal ke badlay """
  16,33,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ab jo yeh log intzaar kar rahay hain to iss ke siwa ab aur kya baqi reh gaya hai ke mulaika hi aa pohnchain, ya tairay rab ka faisla sadir ho jaye? iss terhan ki dhatai inn se pehlay bohat se log kar chuke hain phir jo kuch unn ke sath howa woh unn par Allah ka zulm nah tha balkay unn ka apna zulm tha jo onhon ne khud apne oopar kya"
  16,34,unn ke krtoton ki kharabian aakhir unn ki damangeer ho gayeen aur wohi cheez unn par musallat ho kar rahi jis ka woh mazaq uraya karte thay
  16,35,"yeh mushriqeen kehte hain"" agar Allah chahta to nah hum aur nah hamaray baap dada uss ke siwa kisi aur ki ibadat karte aur nah uss ke hukum ke baghair kisi cheez ko haraamtehratay"" aisay hi bahanay inn se pehlay ke log bhi banatay rahay hain to kya Rasolo-n par saaf saaf baat pouncha dainay ke siwa aur bhi koi zimma daari hai ?"
  16,36,"hum ne har ummat mein aik rasool bhaij diya, aur uss ke zareya se sab ko khabardaar kar diya ke"" Allah ki bandagi karo aur Taghoot ki bandagi se bachcho"" is ke baad un mein se kisi ko Allah ne hadaayat bakhsh aur kisi par zallatmusallat ho gayi phir zara zameen mein chal phir kar dekh lau ke jhutlanay walon ka kya injaam ho chuka hai"
  16,37,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum chahay inn ki hadaayat ke liye kitney hi harees ho, magar Allah jis ko bhatka deta hai phir usay hadaayat nahi diya karta aur is terhan ke logon ki madad koi nahi kar sakta"
  16,38,"yeh log Allah ke naam se kari kari kasmain kha kar kehte hain ke"" Allah kisi marnay walay ko phir se zindah kar ke nah uthaye ga"" uthaye ga kyun nahi, yeh to aik wada hai jisay poora karna is ne apne oopar wajib kar liya hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  16,39,aur aisa hona is liye zurori hai ke Allah inn ke samnay uss haqeeqat ko khol day jis ke baray mein yeh ikhtilaaf kar rahay hain aur munkareen haq ko maloom ho jaye ke woh jhutay thay
  16,40,"( raha is ka imkaan to ) hamein kisi cheez ko wujood mein laane ke liye is se ziyada kuch karna nahi hota ke usay hukum den"" ho ja"" aur bas woh ho jati hai"
  16,41,jo log zulm sehney ke baad Allah ki khatir hijrat kar gay hain un ko hum duniya hi mein acha thikana den ge aur akhirat ka ajar to bohat bara hai kash jaan len woh mazloom
  16,42,jinhon ne sabr kya hai aur jo apne rab ke bharoosay par kaam kar rahay hain ( ke kaisa acha injaam unn ka muntazir hai )
  16,43,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tum se pehlay bhi jab kabhi rasool beje hain aadmi hi beje hain jin ki taraf hum apne paighamaat wahi kya karte thay ahal zikar se pooch lau agar tum log khud nahi jantay"
  16,44,"pichlle Rasolo-n ko bhi hum ne roshan nishanain aur kitaaben day kar bheja tha, aur ab yeh zikar tum par nazil kya hai taakay tum logon ke samnay uss taleem ki tashreeh o tozeeh karte jao jo unn ke liye utari gayi hai, aur taakay log ( khud bhi ) ghhor o fikar karen"
  16,45,"phir kya woh log jo ( dawat paighambar ki mukhalfat mein ) badter se badter chaalein chal rahay hain iss baat se bilkul hi be khauf ho gay hain ke Allah un ko zameen mein dhansa day, ya aisay gooshay mein un par azaab le aeye jidhar se is ke anay ka un ko vahm o gumaan taq nah ho"
  16,46,"ya achanak chaltay phirtay un ko pakar le, ya aisi haalat mein inhen pakdae jabkay inhen khud anay wali museebat ka khatka laga howa ho aur woh is se bachney ki fikar mein chokannay hon ?"
  16,47,woh jo kuch bhi karna chahay yeh log is ko aajiz karne ki taaqat nahi rakhtay haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhara rab bara hi naram khoo aur Raheem hai
  16,48,aur kya yeh log Allah ki peda ki hui kisi cheez ko bhi nahi dekhte ke is ka saya kis terhan Allah ke huzoor sajda karte hue dayen aur baen girta hai? sab ke sab iss terhan izhaar ijaz kar rahay hain
  16,49,zameen aur asmano mein jis qader jaan daar makhloqaat hain aur jitne mulaika hain sab Allah ke agay sir bsjod hain woh hargiz sar kashi nahi karte
  16,50,"apne rab se jo unn ke oopar hai, drtay hain aur jo kuch hukum diya jata hai isi ke mutabiq kaam karte hain"
  16,51,"Allah ka farmaan hai ke"" do khuda nah bana lau, khuda to bas aik hi hai, lehaza tum mujhi se daro"
  16,52,"usi ka hai woh sab kuch jo asmano mein hai aur jo zameen mein hai, aur khalisan usi ka deen ( saari kaayenaat mein ) chal raha hai phir kya Allah ko chore kar tum kisi aur se taqwa karo ge ?"
  16,53,tum ko jo Nemat bhi haasil hai Allah hi ki taraf se hai phir jab koi sakht waqt tum par aata hai to tum log khud apni faryadain le kar usi ki taraf dorrtay ho
  16,54,magar jab Allah is waqt ko taall deta hai to yaka yak tum mein se aik giroh apne rab ke sath dosaron ko ( is meharbani ke shkrie mein ) shareek karne lagta hai
  16,55,"taakay Allah ke ahsaan ki nashukri kere acha, mazay kar lau, anqareeb tumhe maloom ho jaye ga"
  16,56,"yeh log jin ki haqeeqat se waaqif nahi hain unn ke hissay hamaray diye hue rizaq mein se muqarrar karte hain khuda ki qasam, zaroor tum se poocha jaye ga ke yeh jhoot tum ne kaisay ghurr liye thay ?"
  16,57,yeh khuda ke liye betiyan tajweez karte hain subhan Allah ! aur inn ke liye woh jo yeh khud chahain ?
  16,58,jab inn mein se kisi ko beti ke peda honay ki khush khaberi di jati hai to uss ke chehray par clons(ghum ki sihyai) chhaa jati hai aur woh bas khoon ka sa ghoont pi kar reh jata hai
  16,59,logon se chupta phirta hai ke iss buri khabar ke baad kya kisi ko mun dukhaay sochta hai ke zillat ke sath beti ko liye rahay ya matti mein daba day? dekho kaisay buray hukum hain jo yeh khuda ke baray mein lagatay hain
  16,60,"buri sifaat se mutsif kiye jaane ke Laiq to woh log hain jo akhirat ka yaqeen nahi rakhtay raha Allah , to uss ke liye sab se bartar sifaat hain, wohi to sab par ghalib aur hikmat mein kaamil hai"
  16,61,"agar kahin Allah logon ko unn ki zayad-ti par foran hi pakar liya kar taa to roye zameen par kisi mutnaqas ko nah chhorta lekin woh sab ko aik waqt muqarrar taq mohlat deta hai, phir jab woh waqt aa jata hai to is se koi aik gharri bhar bhi agay peechay nahi ho sakta"
  16,62,"aaj yeh log woh cheezein Allah ke liye tajweez kar rahay hain jo khud apne liye aِnhin napasand hain, aur jhoot kehti hain inn ki zubanain ke inn ke liye bhala hi bhala hai inn ke liye to aik hi cheez hai, aur woh hai dozakh ki aag zaroor yeh sab se pehlay uss mein p_hnchaye jayen ge"
  16,63,"khuda ki qasam, ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay bhi bohat si qomon mein hum rasool bhaij chuke hain ( aur pehlay bhi yahi hota raha hai ke ) shetan ne unn ke buray kartoot unhen khushnuma bana kar dukhaay ( aur Rasolo-n ki baat unhon ne maan kar nah di ) wohi shetan aaj inn logon ka bhi sarparast bana howa hai aur yeh dard naak saza ke mustahiq ban rahay hain"
  16,64,hum ne yeh kitaab tum par is liye nazil ki hai ke tum unn ikhtilafat ki haqeeqat inn par khol do jin mein yeh parre hue hain yeh kitaab rahnumai aur rehmat ban kar utri hai unn logon ke liye jo isay maan len
  16,65,( tum har barsaat mein dekhte ho ke ) Allah ne aasman se pani barsaya aur yaka yak murda pari hui zameen mein uss ki badolat jaan daal di yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai suneney walon ke liye
  16,66,"aur tumahray liye maweshion mein bhi aik sabaq mojood hai unn ke pait se gobar aur khoon ke darmain hum aik cheez tumhe pilate hain, yani khalis doodh, jo peenay walon ke liye nihayat khoo sh gawaar hai"
  16,67,( isi terhan ) khajoor ke darakhton aur angoor ki belon se bhi hum aik cheez tumhe pilate hain jisay tum nasha aawar bhi bana letay ho aur pak rizaq bhi yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai aqal se kaam lainay walon ke liye
  16,68,"aur dekho, tumahray rab ne shehad ki makhi par yeh baat wahi kar di ke pahoron mein, aur darakhton mein, aur tatkyun par charhai hui belon mein"
  16,69,apne chattay bana aur har terhan ke phalon ka ras choos aur apne rab ki hamwar ki hui raahon par chalti reh iss makhi ke andar se rang barang ka aik sharbat nikalta hai jis mein Shifa hai logon ke liye yaqeenan is mein bhi aik nishani hai unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar karte hain
  16,70,"aur dekho, Allah ne tum ko peda kya, phir woh tum ko mout deta hai, aur tum mein se koi bad tareen Umar ko pouncha diya jata hai taakay sab kuch jan-nay ke baad phir kuch nah jaane haq yeh hai ke Allah hi ilm mein bhi kaamil hai aur qudrat mein bhi"
  16,71,"aur dekho, Allah ne tum mein se baaz ko baaz par rizaq mein fazeelat ataa ki hai phir jin logon ko yeh fazeelat di gayi hai woh aisay nahi hain ke apna rizaq apne ghulamoo ki taraf phair diya karte hon taakay dono is rizaq mein barabar ke hissa daar ban jayen to kya Allah hi ka ahsaan maan-ne se inn logon ko inkaar hai ?"
  16,72,aur woh Allah hi hai jis ne tumahray liye tumhari hum jins biwiyan banayen aur isi ne un biwion se tumhe betay potay ataa kiye aur achi achi cheezein tumhe khanay ko den phir kya yeh log ( yeh sab kuch dekhte aur jantay hue bhi ) baatil ko mantay hain aur Allah ke ahsaan ka inkaar karte hain
  16,73,aur Allah ko chore kar unn ko pujte hain jin ke haath mein nah asmano se inhen kuch bhi rizaq dena hai nah zameen se aur nah yeh kaam woh kar hi satke hain ?
  16,74,"pas Allah ke liye misalein nah gharo, Allah jaanta hai, tum nahi jantay"
  16,75,"Allah aik misaal deta hai aik to hai ghulam, jo dosray ka mamlook hai aur khud koi ikhtiyar nahi rakhta dosra shakhs aisa hai jisay hum ne apni taraf se acha rizaq ataa kya hai aur woh is mein se khulay aur chupay khoob kharch karta hai batao, kya yeh dono barabar hain?sab khobyan Akllah ko hai, magar aksar log ( is seedhi baat ko ) nahi jantay"
  16,76,"Allah aik aur misaal deta hai do aadmi hain aik goonga berha hai, koi kaam nahi kar sakta, apne aaqa par boojh bana howa hai, jidhar bhi woh usay beje koi bhala kaam uss se ban nah aeye dosra shakhs aisa hai ke insaaf ka hukum deta hai aur khud raah raast par qaim hai batao kya yeh dono yaksaa hain ?"
  16,77,"aur zameen o aasman ke posheeda haqayiq ka ilm to Allah hi ko hai aur qayamat ke barpaa honay ka maamla kuch der nah le ga magar bas itni ke jis mein aadmi ki palak jhapak jaye, balkay is se bhi kuch kam haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah sab kuch kar sakta hai"
  16,78,"Allah ne tum ko tumhari maaon ke piton se nikala is haalat mein ke tum kuch nah jantay thay uss ne tumhe kaan diye, ankhen den, aur sochnay walay dil diye, is liye ke tum shukar guzaar bano"
  16,79,kya inn logon ne kabhi parindon ko nahi dekha ke fazayaasmani mein kisi terhan maskhar hain? Allah ke siwa kis ne inn ko thaam rakha hai? iss mein bohat nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo imaan laatay hain
  16,80,"Allah ne tumahray liye tumahray gharon ko jaye sukoon banaya is ne janwaron ki khaalon se tumahray liye aisay makaan peda kiye jinhein tum safar aur qiyam, dono halaton mein halka paate ho uss ne janwaron ke sof aur oon aur balon se tumahray liye pahannay aur baratnay ki bohat si cheezein peda kar den jo zindagi ki muddat muqarara taq tumahray kaam aati hain"
  16,81,"is ne apni peda ki hui bohat si cheezon se tumahray liye saaye ka intizam kya, pahoron mein tumahray liye panah gahin banayen, aur tumhe aisi poshakain bakhsheen jo tumhe garmi se bachati hain aur kuch doosri poshakain jo aapas ki jung mein tumhari hifazat karti hain is terhan woh tum par apni nematon ki takmeel karta hai shayad ke tum farmaa bardaar bano"
  16,82,"ab agar yeh log mun morty hain to ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum par saaf saaf pegham haq pouncha dainay ke siwa aur koi zimma daari nahi hai"
  16,83,"yeh Allah ke ahsaan ko pehchante hain, phir is ka inkaar karte hain aur inn mein besh tar log aisay hain jo haq maan-ne ke liye tayyar nahi hain"
  16,84,"( aِnhin kuch hosh bhi hai ke uss roz kya banay gi ) jabkay hum har ummat mein se aik gawah khara karen ge, phir kafiroon ko nah hujjatain paish karne ka mauqa diya jaayegaa nah un se tauba o astaghfar hi ka mutalba kya jaye ga"
  16,85,zalim log jab aik dafaa azaab dekh len ge to is ke baad nah unn ke azaab mein koi takhfeef ki jaye gi aur nah inhen aik lamha bhar ki mohlat di jaye gi
  16,86,"aur jab woh log jinhon ne duniya mein shirk kya tha apne tehra-ay hue sharikon ko dekhen ge to kahin ge"" ae parvar-digaar, yahi hain hamaray woh shareek jinhein hum tujhe chore kar puraka karte thay"" is par unn ke woh mabood inhen saaf jawab den ge ke"" tum jhutay ho """
  16,87,uss waqt yeh sab Allah ke agay jhuk jayen ge aur un ki woh saari aftara-pardaziyan )bohtan bazi) rafo chakkar ho jayen gi jo yeh duniya mein karte rahay thay
  16,88,jin logon ne khud kufar ki raah ikhtiyar ki aur dosaron ko Allah ki raah se roka inhen hum azaab par azaab den ge uss fasaad ke badlay jo woh duniya mein barpaa karte rahay
  16,89,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, aِnhin uss din se khabardaar kar do ) jab ke hum har ummat mein khud usi ke andar se aik gawah utha khara karen ge jo uss ke muqablay mein shahadat day ga, aur inn logon ke muqablay mein shahadat dainay ke liye hum tumhe layein ge aur ( yeh isi shahadat ki tayari hai ke ) hum ne yeh kitaab tum par nazil kar di hai jo har cheez ki saaf saaf wazahat karne wali hai aur hadaayat o rehmat aur basharat hai unn logon ke liye jinhon ne sir tasleem khham kar diya hai"
  16,90,Allah Adal aur ahsaan aur sila rehmi ka hukum deta hai aur badi o be hiyai aur zulm o zayad-ti se mana karta hai woh tumhe nasiyaat karta hai taakay tum sabaq lau
  16,91,"Allah ke ehad ko poora karo jabkay tum ne is se koi ehad baandha ho, aur apni kasmain pukhta karne ke baad toar nah daalo jabkay tum Allah ko apne oopar gawah bana chuke ho Allah tumahray sab af-aal se bakhabar hai"
  16,92,"tumhari haalat uss aurat ki si nah ho jaye jis ne aap hi mehnat se soot kata aur phir aap hi usay tukre tukre kar dala tum apni qasmon ko aapas ke mamlaat mein makr o fraib ka hathyaar banatay ho taakay aik qoum doosri qoum se barh kar faiday haasil kere halan ke Allah is ehad o Paiman ke zareya se tum ko azmaish mein dalta hai, aur zaroor woh qayamat ke roz tumahray tamam ikhtilafat ki haqeeqat tum par khol day ga"
  16,93,"agar Allah ki Mushiyat yeh hoti ( ke tum mein koi ikhtilaaf nah ho ) to woh tum sab ko aik hi ummat bana deta, magar woh jisay chahta hai gumraahi mein dalta hai aur jisay chahta hai raah raast dikha deta hai, aur zaroor tum se tumahray aamaal ki baz purse ho kar rahay gi"
  16,94,"( aur ae mslmano, ) tum apni qasmon ko aapas mein aik dosray ko dhoka dainay ka zareya nah bana lena, kahin aisa nah ho ke koi qadam jamnay ke baad akhar jaye aur tum iss jurm ki Padaash mein ke tum ne logon ko Allah ki raah se roka, bura nateeja dekho aur sakht saza bhgto"
  16,95,"Allah ke ehad ko thoray se faiday ke badlay nah beech daalo, jo kuch Allah ke paas hai woh tumahray liye ziyada behtar hai agar tum jano"
  16,96,"jo kuch tumahray paas hai woh kharch ho jaane wala hai aur jo kuch Allah ke paas hai wohi baqi rehne wala hai, aur hum zaroor sabr se kaam lainay walon ko unn ke ajar unn ke behtareen aamaal ke mutabiq den ge"
  16,97,"jo shakhs bhi naik amal kere ga, khuwa woh mard ho ya aurat, basharteh kehho woh momin, usay hum duniya mein pakeeza zindagi busr karayen ge aur ( akhirat mein ) aisay logon ko un ke ajar un ke behtareen aamaal ke mutabiq bakhsheen ge"
  16,98,phir jab tum quran parhnay lagu to shetan rjim se khuda ki panah maang liya karo
  16,99,ussay unn logon par tasallut haasil nahi hota jo imaan laatay aur apne rab par bhrosa karte hain
  16,100,is ka zor to unhi logon par chalta hai jo is ko apna sarparast banatay aur is ke behkanay se shirk karte hain
  16,101,jab hum aik aayat ki jagah doosri aayat nazil karte hain aur Allah behtar jaanta hai ke woh kya nazil kere to yeh log kehte hain ke tum yeh quran khoo daal ghurr te ho asal baat yeh hai ke inn mein se aksar log haqeeqat se nawaqif hain
  16,102,inn se kaho ke isay to rooh al quds ne theek theek mere rab ki taraf se batadreej nazil kya hai taakay imaan laane walon ke imaan ko pukhta kere aur farmaa bardaroon ko zindagi ke mamlaat mein seedhi raah betaye aur unhen Falah o Saadat ki khush khaberi day
  16,103,hamein maloom hai yeh log tumahray mutaliq kehte hain ke is shakhs ko aik aadmi sakata paratha hai halaank un ka ishara jis aadmi ki taraf hai is ki zabaan ajmi hai aur yeh saaf arabi zabaan hai
  16,104,haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log Allah ki ayaat ko nahi mantay Allah kabhi un ko sahih baat taq pounchanay ki tofeq nahi deta aur aisay logon ke liye dard naak azaab hai
  16,105,"( jhooti baatein naya nahi ghurr taa balkay ) jhoot woh log ghurr rahay hain, jo Allah ki ayaat ko nahi mantay, wohi haqeeqat mein jhutay hain"
  16,106,jo shakhs imaan laane ke baad kufar kere ( woh agar ) majaboor kya gaya ho aur dil is ka imaan par mutmaen ho ( tab to kher ) magar jis ne dil ki Raza mandi se kufar ko qubool kar liya is par Allah ka ghazab hai aur aisay sab logon ke liye bara azaab hai
  16,107,"yeh is liye ke onhon ne akhirat ke muqaabla mein duniya ki zindagi ko pasand kar liya, aur Allah ka qaida hai ke woh unn logon ko raah nijaat nahi dekhata jo uss ki Nemat ka kufran karen"
  16,108,yeh woh log hain jin ke dilon aur kaanon aur aankhon par Allah ne mohar laga di hai yeh ghaflat mein doob chuke hain
  16,109,zaroor hai ke akhirat mein yahi khasaray mein rahen
  16,110,"bakhilaf is ke jin logon ka haal yeh hai ke jab ( imaan laane ki wajah se ) woh sataye gay to onhon ne ghar baar chore diye, hijrat ki, raah khuda mein sakhtiyaan jhelen aur sbrse kaam liya, unn ke liye yaqeenan tera rab ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  16,111,( inn sab ka faisla uss din hoga ) jab ke har mutnaqas apne hi bachao ki fikar mein laga howa hoga aur har aik ko is ke kiye ka badla poora poora diya jaye ga aur kisi par zarra barabar zulm nah honay paye ga
  16,112,Allah aik bastii ki misaal deta hai woh aman o itminan ki zindagi busr kar rahi thi aur har taraf se is ko bafrazat rizaq poanch raha tha ke uss ne Allah ki nematon ka kufran shuru kar diya tab Allah ne is ke bashindon ko unn ke krtoton ka yeh maza chakhaaya ke bhook aur khauf ki museebatein un par chhaa gayeen
  16,113,unn ke paas un ki apni qoum mein se aik rasool aaya magar onhon ne is ko jhutla diya aakhir-kaar azaab ne unn ko aa liya jabkay woh zalim ho chuke thay
  16,114,"pas ae logo, Allah ne jo kuch halal aur pak rizaq tum ko bakhsha hai ussay khao aur Allah ke ahsaan ka shukar ada karo agar tum waqai usi ki bandagi karne walay ho"
  16,115,"Allah ne jo kuch tum par haraam kya hai woh hai Murdaar aur khoon aur soor ka gosht aur woh janwar jis par Allah ke siwa kisi aur ka naam liya gaya ho Albata bhook se majaboor ho kar agar koi inn cheezon ko kha le, baghair is ke ke woh qanoon Ellahi ki khilaaf warzi ka khwahish mand ho, ya hadd zaroorat se tajawaz ka murtakib ho, to yaqeenan Allah maaf karne aur reham frmane wala hai"
  16,116,"aur yeh jo tumhari zubanain jhutay ehkaam lagaya karti hain ke yeh cheez halal hai aur woh haraam, to is terhan ke hukum laga kar Allah par jhoot nah baandha karo jo log Allah par jhutay aftara bandhte hain woh hargiz Falah nahi paaya karte"
  16,117,duniya ka aish chand roza hai aakhir kaar unn ke liye dard naak saza hai
  16,118,woh cheezein hum ne khaas tor par yahudion ke liye haraam ki theen jin ka zikar hum is se pehlay tum se kar chuke hain aur yeh unn par hamara zulm nah tha balkay unn ka apna hi zulm tha jo woh apne oopar kar rahay thay
  16,119,Albata jin logon ne jahalat ki bana par bura amal kya aur phir tauba kar ke apne amal ki islaah kar li to yaqeenan tauba o islaah ke baad tera rab unn ke liye ghafoor aur Raheem hai
  16,120,"waqea yeh hai ke ibrahim apni zaat se aik poori ummat tha, Allah ka Mutee farmaan aur yak so woh kabhi mushriq nah tha"
  16,121,Allah ki nematon ka shukar ada karne wala tha Allah ne is ko muntakhib kar liya aur seedha rasta dekhaya
  16,122,duniya mein is ko bhalai di aur akhirat mein woh yaqeenan salheen mein se hoga
  16,123,phir hum ne tumhari taraf yeh wahi bhaije ke yak so ho kar ibrahim ke tareeqay par chalo aur woh mushrikon mein se nah tha
  16,124,"raha sabt, to woh hum ne unn logon par musallat kya tha jinhon ne is ke ehkaam mein ikhtilaaf kya, aur yaqeenan tera rab qayamat ke roz un sab baton ka faisla kar day ga jin mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain"
  16,125,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apne rab ke rastay ki taraf dawat do hikmat aur umdah nasiyaat ke sath, aur logon se mobahisa karo aisay tareeqa par jo behtareen ho tumhara rab hi ziyada behtar jaanta hai ke kon is ki raah se bhatka howa hai aur kon raah raast par hai"
  16,126,aur agar tum log badla lau to bas isi qader le lau jis qader tum par zayad-ti ki gayi ho lekin agar tum sabr karo to yaqeenan yeh sabr karne walon hi ke haq mein behtar hai
  16,127,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, sabr se kaam kiye jao aur tumhara yeh sabr Allah hi ki tofeq se hai inn logon ki harkaat par ray nj nah karo aur nah un ki chaal bazyon par dil tang ho"
  16,128,Allah unn logon ke sath hai jo taqwa se kaam letay hain aur ahsaan par amal karte hain
